Titolo: Atelier Iris: Eternal Mana

Anno: 2004

Descrizione: Atelier Iris: Eternal Mana is a role-playing video game developed by Japanese developer Gust for the PlayStation 2, the first of the Atelier Iris saga. Despite the Atelier series' long run and popularity in Japan, Atelier Iris was the first of the series to be released in the U.S.; this release and the English translation were done by NIS America. Japanese voice-overs can be enabled.